<catsoop-section>Project Overview</catsoop-section>

In this project, you'll build a **compact digital clock** that:
- Displays time in **HH:MM:SS** format (hours:minutes:seconds)
- Uses **six 7-segment displays** (2 for hours, 2 for minutes, 2 for seconds)
- Counts seconds automatically using a **555 timer** or **crystal oscillator**
- Resets seconds and minutes at **60**
- Resets hours at **12**
- Has **buttons to set the time** manually

